{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3242500/extras/Quantum_Curse_Banner_01.png?t=1739475151\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3242500/extras/Quantum_Curse_Banner_02.png?t=1739475151\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3242500/extras/Quantum_Curse_Banner_03.png?t=1739475151\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Awake as an experiment unbeknownst as to its origin.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Imbued with access to super computers and quantum state manipulation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Escape a mysterious abandoned laboratory.  <br>Manipulate, entangled quantum experiments.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Run, jump, shoot, explore, solve puzzles, backtrack and collect power ups.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Discover what you are.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore 10 themed laboratory regions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Find mobility enhancements, blaster power-ups and key items to allow access to previously inaccessible areas.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Shoot to kill a multitude of mutant threats and abominations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Dodge traps and maneuver through various hazards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Seek to find 50 quantum computer access ports.\u00a0 Enter the quantum environment to manipulate blocks and particles tied to you own movements, destroy the particle experiments and disable each of the 50 quantum ports.\u00a0\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Escape the laboratory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3242500?t=1739475151","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3242500/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1739475151","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamst